e willing to devote large fractions of their lives to one another, and wrist watches would allow you to be able to measure that fraction of life all the way down to the second.</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A Customized Piece of Anniversary Jewelry</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">She stands out from the rest of the world in your eyes, so she should stand out from the rest of the world in the eyes of her friends and others, too. One of the most heartfelt ways to do that is to get her something that literally no one else on the planet has and get her a </span><a href=\"https://www.itshot.com/jewelry/custom-made\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">customized piece of jewelry</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> that she can call her very own. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Now, you might be thinking that a cheaper way to do this is just to get her a monogrammed towel or a screen printed tee shirt, but those cheap, sometimes tawdry-looking items cannot possibly compare to the awe she would feel opening a box to a pendant customized by you just for her. Anyone can get any of the items I have written above for the woman they love, but the woman you love and have loved long enough to celebrate an anniversary with beautiful jewelry is different. She deserves something that took you time to create, something that you put more thought into than just clicking a box. She deserves this, and you know that. So dont be afraid to get it for her because she is worth it and you both know it.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">But it doesnt even have to be a pendant! The beauty in investing in a customized piece of jewelry is that nothing else on Earth would be like it, just like no one else on Earth is like her. It will also hold a special place in her heart because not just anyone designed it, either. YOU designed it, one of the people she loves and cherishes every single day. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There is a huge difference in having the piece come from a collection that anyone can buy from versus having the piece come from a place in your heart, a place that really only she can touch. And that difference means the entire universe to her, just like she means the entire universe to you.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hopefully this guide helped you realize the perfect piece of jewelry to get for your dearly beloved. No matter what darling piece you choose from this guide, she is bound to thank you lovingly and think of you every time she sees it in her jewelry box, and every time she wears it after that. And who knows, maybe next anniversary she will return the favor by buying you a nice piece of jewelry as well! Come back next year to find yet another perfect present for that perfect special someone in your life.</span>','Anniversary Jewelry Ideas Your Partner Will Love','','inherit','closed','closed','','116-revision-v1','','','2018-11-15 19:49:58','2018-11-15 19:49:58','',116,'https://www.itshot.com/blog/116-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(120,1,'2019-01-03 19:41:11','2019-01-03 19:41:11','<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In todays world, you really can have anything you want and jewelry is no different. You know about diamonds, or at least you know of white diamonds. What you may not realize is that there are </span><a href=\"https://www.itshot.com/jewelry/womens-rings/diamond/colored\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">colored diamonds, </span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">too. This opens up a whole new world of opportunities in regards to your jewelry box, the types of looks you can create with jewelry, and the bejeweled gifts that you can give for every special occasion. So, without any further ado, lets explore a new option in regards to jewelry, the canary yellow diamond--a gem that celebrities rave about. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">While colored diamonds have been on the market for years, they are growing in popularity because of their exotic look. In the past, when someone wanted to wear colored jewelry, they thought their only option was to use Topaz, Emeralds, or Sapphires. Celebrities brought colored diamonds to the forefront of fashion. </span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-121 alignright\" src=\"https://www.itshot.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/ladies-natural-yellow-diamond-ring-139ct-14k-gold-halo-design_wh.jpg\" alt=\"ladies-natural-yellow-diamond-ring-139ct-14k-gold-halo-design_wh\" width=\"210\" height=\"210\" />Celebrities Love Them</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Marilyn Monroe was the celebrity who started the yellow trend. She famously wore a necklace with a 24 carat canary yellow diamond to a premiere in Hollywood. Since that day, stars have loved them and they have been wearing them ever since. At any star studded event, you can probably find a star wearing canary yellow diamonds somewhere as part of his or her look. Canary diamonds have been featured in everything from pendants to earrings to even being sewn into dresses and suits.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Jennifer Lopez is a more modern sensation who is known to be a yellow diamond lover. She wears them regularly and was even given one for the birth of her twins. Carrie Underwood is another star rocking yellow. Her engagement ring is a 5 carat yellow diamond. Heidi Klum also was given a canary diamond for her </span><a href=\"https://www.itshot.com/jewelry/engagement-rings\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">engagement ring</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">All of the celebrities chose the canary yellow diamond because it adds an element of class and pizazz. Famous people are always trying to make themselves stand out, which can be hard in their world. With white diamonds, they focus on how big it is. Now the focus is how different it can be besides just the carat. Thats where this unique color comes in. </span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What to Look For in Canary Yellow Diamonds</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When shopping for diamonds, there is more to them besides the appearance to the naked eye. There are </span><a href=\"https://www.itshot.com/education-guides/jewelry/diamond-buying-guide\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">four Cs of diamonds</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: color, clarity, cut, and carat. These are crucial to understand before purchasing diamonds. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Color for white diamonds in particular has to do with how colorless it is. The less color, the more expensive. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Clarity speaks for its </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">natural inclusions or lack of. The higher that clarity, the more expensive. Natural inclusings are flaws, like traces of minerals, that may be seen with or without a microscope.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The cut of the diamond can be in Princess, Round, Emerald, or Baguette. What makes the cut important is not just the shape, but the craftsmanship of the cut. A bad cut can ruin a diamond. A good cut will enhance the way the light travels through it which creates the shine and sparkle. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Carat refers to the size. Diamonds are measured in carats. In the diamond world, the bigger the better. </span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What Makes Them Special</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">These diamonds not only stand out on you, but they stand out in the world of diamonds, too. How many times had you heard of canary yellow diamonds before reading this article? Probably not many.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Everyone has white diamonds, classic but common. Chocolate and champagne diamonds are still a popular trend. You\'ve probably seen those stones many times. Canary yellow diamonds stand apart from their peers, because you dont see them often in peoples accessories. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">People notice canary yellow diamond pieces right away. These sunshine stones will help brighten any outfit, turning an outfit with bland, neutral colors into the perfect backdrop for this splash of color. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">One good example would be wearing a black and white professional looking outfit to go to work, but then adding a canary yellow pop of color. Yellow diamonds are a way to add a bit of personality and fun to any wardrobe, while maintaining a professional, classy appearance. Even if your outfit has a lot of color already, these gorgeous gemstones will perfectly match the brightness of your ensemble.</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-122 alignleft\" src=\"https://www.itshot.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/natural-yellow-diamond-ring-335ct-14k-pave-p-40942.jpg\" alt=\"natural-yellow-diamond-ring-335ct-14k-pave-p-40942\" width=\"210\" height=\"210\" />They Make Excellent Gifts</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Canary yellow diamonds are the perfect color of diamond because they are gender neutral. Yellow diamonds can adorn everything from watch faces to wedding rings, so the options are limitless. It doesnt matter whether the person that you are buying the piece of jewelry for is masculine or feminine, canary diamonds work for either.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Although not worn often, canary diamonds are actually some of the most common colored diamonds found in nature. They are also some of the clearest diamonds found in nature, meaning that it will have a true yellow hue that stands out from the rest of the diamonds out there.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Canary yellow diamonds make wonderful gifts because they are so different from the other types of stones out there. White diamonds are beautiful, pearls are sophisticated, sapphires stunning, rubies are rich, but with the canary yellow diamond, its totally different. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">These stones have such a unique look. The can be classic, beautiful, sophisticated and stunning all in one diamond. This makes them an investment that you can be sure of. </span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">They Pair Well With Other Jewels</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In deciding what piece of jewelry you want next, think diversity. Yellow diamonds pair especially well with amethysts or purple gemstones because yellow and purple are complementary colors, meaning that between the two of them, they use all of the primary colors and look great together. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">They can also pair well with any given birthstone, meaning that you can buy yourself a birthday treat and make it especially bright and fun by having your jeweler add canary diamonds to your piece.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For a fun look, try wearing a monochromatic blue outfit with a canary yellow necklace and a ruby ring. This way, all of the primary colors stand out in one single, cohesive look. It creates a nice, bright ensemble that can shake up any wardrobe. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Try the same thing with warm colors, wearing red and then combining that with a canary yellow bracelet and a </span><a href=\"https://www.itshot.com/jewelry/womens-necklaces/diamond/black\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">black diamond necklace</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">They Are a Great Investment</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Canary yellow diamonds do not require any special maintenance, nor do they fade with respect to time. This means that even if you never get your canary yellow jewelry pieces professionally cleaned, something that you should do with other jewelry to prolong the appealing look of it, the look of these pieces will never suffer. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">However, if you do get your pieces professionally cleaned, the jewelry would probably appreciate it! So if you are someone who is into low maintenance things and like to lead a low maintenance lifestyle, then canary yellow diamonds are the perfect accessory that you may not have even known existed.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Because canary yellow diamonds retain their look, they are pieces that can be passed down from generation to generation as a secure investment for the future. Like gold and other previous materials, yellow diamonds are valuable to have in times of financial crisis because they keep their value. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">All the other colors of diamond that exist out there are beautiful in their own ways, but a canary yellow diamond is a force to be reckoned with. They have stood strongly as the fashion trend of celebrities for many years, and that doesnt see to be going anywhere any time soon. While </span><a href=\"https://www.itshot.com/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">looking for the perfect piece of jewelry</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, remember the four Cs.</span>','Why Choose a Canary Yellow Diamond?','','publish','closed','closed','','why-choose-a-canary-yellow-diamond','','','2019-01-21 19:41:50','2019-01-21 19:41:50','',0,'https://www.itshot.com/blog/?p=120',0,'post','',0),(121,1,'2018-11-15 19:56:12','2018-11-15 19:56:12','','ladies-natural-yellow-diamond-ring-139ct-14k-gold-halo-design_wh','','inherit','closed','closed','','ladies-natural-yellow-diamond-ring-139ct-14k-gold-halo-design_wh','','','2018-11-15 19:56:17','2018-11-15 19:56:17','',120,'https://www.itshot.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/ladies-natural-yellow-diamond-ring-139ct